<!-- HOW WE DO IT -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tighter mb-4">How We Do It</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary max-w-3xl mb-10">Our six-step process ensures proper adhesion and a durable, factory-quality finish on every vanity we respray.</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">1</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Remove Doors &amp; Drawers</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">All doors, drawers, and hardware are carefully removed so every surface can be properly prepared and sprayed. Hinges and handles are set aside for reinstallation or replacement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">2</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Clean, Sand &amp; Prep All Surfaces</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Every surface is thoroughly cleaned to remove grease, soap residue, and contaminants. All panels are sanded to create a profile for the primer to grip. This step is critical for long-term adhesion.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">3</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Fill Any Chips or Damage</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Chips, dents, and surface imperfections are filled and sanded smooth. This ensures the final sprayed finish is even and flawless with no visible defects showing through.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">4</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Apply Bonding Primer</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">A bonding primer specifically suited to your vanity's surface type is applied. This is the foundation of a lasting finish &mdash; the primer creates a chemical bond between the surface and the topcoat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">5</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Spray Professional Two-Part Coating</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Multiple coats of professional two-part coating are spray-applied in your chosen colour. Spray application delivers the smooth, even factory finish that brush or roller painting simply cannot achieve.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">6</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Rehang Doors &amp; Install Hardware</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Doors and drawers are carefully rehung with adjusted hinges. If you've opted for new handles, we install those too. The result is a vanity that looks and feels like a brand new unit.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

